geo:GnssReceiver.geo:notes: This receiver is installed for the navigation experiment using ETS-VIII(Engineering Test Satellite-VIII), thus, transmission of GPS data will interrupt when the experiment carry out. The data which received in the experiment period will transmit after the end of experiment.
Reference clock (10MHz) which made by cesium atomic clock is inputed.
